[3] Brazil (Santos, SP)
Date: Fri 2 Apr 2010
Source: Terra [in Portuguese, trans. & summ. Mod.TY, edited]
<http://esportes.terra.com.br/futebol/estaduais/2010/noticias/0,,OI4355664-EI14489,00-Apos+Giovanni+Santos+confirma+mais+seis+casos+de+dengue.html>


[The main focus of this report is that dengue has hit the city of
Santos, and particularly its football (soccer) club, with details
about specific players. Only general observations will be included
here. - Mod.TY]

"Today, the mosquito is scattered throughout the entire city, which
intensifies the proliferation of the mosquito," said the city
Secretary of Health, Odilio Rodriguez. To date, dengue is now treated
as an epidemic in Santos, with 911 cases registered.

